text.text: Nice stadium that allows you to enter to the seats area which has a very nice view of ang mo kio on the left and the unique condominiums on the right. During the weekdays in the late afternoon there are usually secondary schools students who come here to train for their track and field CCA. In case u don't know there is only one entrance to the stadium during non-event time and its located at the lowest level in the middle

text.text:
Watched SPL match between Lion City Saillors FC and Albirex Niigata FC.

Quite a distance from Bishan MRT Station.

Seats in the stands are very compact. Got to be patient if moving in and out of the seats as you will need the other visitors to give way for you to move.

Have a good dining place, in Good Bites.
